              "type": "text",
              "text": "## Canonical User Intent (already disambiguated by LLM)\r\nSet up a listener to receive new messages from a specified messaging target and trigger a goal when a message arrives\n## functions available starts ##\r\n{\"Description\":\"Send and recieve private messages. Get account(public key), set current account for messaging\",\"Methods\":[{\"MethodName\":\"GetPublicKey\",\"Parameters\":[],\"ReturnValue\":{\"Type\":\"System.String\"}},{\"MethodName\":\"GetRelays\",\"Parameters\":[],\"ReturnValue\":{\"Type\":\"System.String\"}},{\"MethodName\":\"SetCurrentAccount\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"publicKeyOrName\",\"IsRequired\":true}]},{\"Description\":\"goalName should be prefixed by ! and be whole word with possible slash(/)\",\"MethodName\":\"Listen\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"PLang.Models.GoalToCallInfo\",\"Name\":\"goalName\",\"Description\":\"(see Type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"contentVariableName\",\"DefaultValue\":\"content\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"senderVariableName\",\"DefaultValue\":\"sender\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"eventVariableName\",\"DefaultValue\":\"__NosrtEventKey__\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Nullable`1[System.DateTimeOffset]\",\"Name\":\"listenFromDateTime\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String[]\",\"Name\":\"onlyMessageFromSenders\",\"IsRequired\":false}]},{\"MethodName\":\"SendPrivateMessageToMyself\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"content\",\"IsRequired\":true}]},{\"MethodName\":\"SendPrivateMessage\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"content\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"receiverPublicKey\",\"IsRequired\":true}]},{\"MethodName\":\"GetPrivateKey\",\"Parameters\":[],\"ReturnValue\":{\"Type\":\"System.String\"}},{\"MethodName\":\"SendEmail\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"PLang.Modules.MessageModule.Program+EmailMessage\",\"Name\":\"emailMessage\",\"Description\":\"(see Type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":true}],\"ReturnValue\":{\"Type\":\"System.Object\"}}],\"SupportingObjects\":[{\"Type\":\"PLang.Models.GoalToCallInfo\",\"Name\":\"goalName\",\"Description\":\"Name of goal and parameters that is called, e.g. in condition, loops, run goal. Keep Name as user defines it with path\",\"TypeProperties\":[{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Name\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2[System.String,System.Object]\",\"Name\":\"Parameters\",\"Description\":\"Name of goal and parameters that is called, e.g. in condition, loops, run goal. Keep Name as user defines it with path\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"WaitForExecution\",\"Description\":\"Whether to wait for the goal to complete before continuing. Default is true.\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Int64\",\"Name\":\"DelayWhenNotWaitingInMilliseconds\",\"Description\":\"Delay in milliseconds when not waiting for execution. Default is 50.\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.UInt32\",\"Name\":\"WaitForXMillisecondsBeforeRunningGoal\",\"Description\":\"Wait for X milliseconds before running the goal. Default is 0.\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"Isolated\",\"Description\":\"Run the goal in an isolated container. Default is false.\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"DisableSystemGoals\",\"Description\":\"Disable system/OS goals when running. Default is false.\",\"IsRequired\":true}],\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"PLang.Modules.MessageModule.Program+EmailMessage\",\"Name\":\"emailMessage\",\"TypeProperties\":[{\"Type\":\"System.Collections.Generic.List`1[System.String]\",\"Name\":\"ToEmails\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Subject\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Body\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"TextBody\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"IsHtml\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Collections.Generic.List`1[System.String]\",\"Name\":\"Cc\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Collections.Generic.List`1[System.String]\",\"Name\":\"Bcc\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"ReplyTo\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2[System.String,System.String]\",\"Name\":\"Headers\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Collections.Generic.List`1[System.Object]\",\"Name\":\"Attachements\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Service\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"FromEmail\",\"IsRequired\":false}],\"IsRequired\":false}]}\r\n## functions available ends ##\r\n## defined variables ##\r\nconfig.NostrAskTarget (type:object), \r\n## defined variables ##\nFollowing Relay servers are available: [\"wss://relay.damus.io\",\"wss://nostr-pub.wellorder.net\",\"wss://offchain.pub\",\"wss://nos.lol\",\"wss://relay.nostr.band\",\"wss://nostr.wine\",\"wss://purplepag.es\"].\r\nFollowing are Nostr accounts:[]\r\n"
